Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.01,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決 斷 之 時
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西也很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐大人 有客人找您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦 讓他過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐「大人」？ 真臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然隨便打開我的貨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候變成得這麼了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我讓他們這麼幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦隆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「將這個地球打造成我等的理想鄉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第二個阿瓦隆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「別猶豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾絲在加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾米在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長話短說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘艦團的人到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都像幽靈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神都像被附身了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的居民肯定也會被變成那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是如此 我當初離開加爾剛蒂亞又有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘願這樣下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人正在打算謀反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是來接我的衝浪龍蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海賊拉凱奇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那就跟那個龍蝦合作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙想指望破廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過雷德那傢伙不會幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就得這樣過一輩子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把帆布展開來收集雨水」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你濕透了呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「會感冒的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前觀測到的稱為「雨」的氣像現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未感知到特殊異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神賜予了我們巨大的恩典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們將前往神的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻上至高的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為生者而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你們要做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為救贖人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而永垂不朽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是為了看這些…而來到這裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個瘋狂的艦團接下來將駛向加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙我果然受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了從希迪亞斯手中保護大家才來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護艾米 為了保護貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護那些人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾中校發令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雷德少尉進入臨戰態勢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「聽從我的指揮」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請貴官進行判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我判斷 你執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我或許從未真正做出過選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解貴官的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校的指令…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 你和Striker的戰力差有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據不足 無法計算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解貴官的提問意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠和Striker戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Striker X3752目前的行為不屬於同盟的軍務範疇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以認定為交戰對象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我能和中校戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對該問題的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已超出本機作為駕駛員支援啟發系統的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何情況下 戰鬥方針的制定均交由貴官判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 使用無線會被攔截
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能直接傳達給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這麼重大的使命 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能飛往加爾剛蒂亞的只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 拯救大家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可欠我一個人情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 進入臨戰態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,partb
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾…剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾剛蒂亞…要被襲擊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人開著衝浪風箏飛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗雅 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保護加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能聽梅露蒂的 改變航路進行避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的立場 不得不這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德讓我們逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算自己去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算代替我們 一個人去戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了保護加爾剛蒂亞 甚至不惜和過去的同伴反目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我們卻要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他作出了選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也必須作出選擇才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾德姆醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特 該是使用那把鑰匙的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身負艦團賢者之任的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依據職責建議艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是使用之時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 希望你也能助我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為讓世界領略我偉大的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領略偉大的神力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣佈 新的聖戰就此打響
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會得到勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為給這個星球帶來絕對的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為將這個星球建設成安寧華貴的理想鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順從於我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是通往恆久幸福的唯一道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 這玩笑可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是同盟戰士該有的發言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是銀河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是人類居住的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的未來是我們的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責任？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顆星球上有著活在這裡的人們所建立的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有理由破壞它！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我等的正義不變」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「別猶豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 這是神之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力怎麼會這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測其威力並非來源於內部發生器 而來源於外部裝備的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保存自身能量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 給這顆星球帶來新的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐 你快撤 這是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你們也不怎麼討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個裝神弄鬼的玩意更讓人不爽一萬倍！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一發 準備好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不參戰的普通居民在裝甲區域內躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船是本艦團的母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能成為攻擊目標 請做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饒恕叛亂 反抗的全都是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我就是這麼粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你還挺男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你另眼相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我踹開他們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以在戰略上確保有利地位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建議採取打即跑戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.48,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(724,650)}Hit-and-run Tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻擊敵機頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺死中校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機的機動性凌駕於本機之上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「無論強者還是弱者」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「均依靠自身的理性相互扶持」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這才能稱為人類吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不是嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我打中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生器 以最大功率輸出！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我說 雷德」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「願不願意與我一起改變這個星球？」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始接近敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸入緊急開倉信號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「還好有你在」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 還願意 跟隨我…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿勢控制系統 重啟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 貴官的抵抗是毫無意義的

